### ğŸ§© **In Summary**

| Concept        | Applies To | Purpose                                    |
| -------------- | ---------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| **Taint**      | Node       | Repels Pods unless tolerated               |
| **Toleration** | Pod        | Allows Pod to be scheduled on tainted node |

